data.description: This is a gated community just steps to the sand. The floor plan called Sandpiper is most desirable in Surfside III. Clubhouse features include a recreation area (pool tables, Ping pong), gym, indoor pool& spa which is heated all year round. In the back of the complex is BBQ areas with children's play area. This could be your beach retreat with the Ocean, fishing pier right outside your door.  AT THIS PRICE! Don't let this opportunity pass you by.
